# Scope Edits and Commands to mkdocs-live-wysiwyg-plugin

All edits and commands must be within `mkdocs-live-wysiwyg-plugin` (or its subdirectories). Do not modify files or run commands outside this directory.

- **Edits**: Only edit files under `mkdocs-live-wysiwyg-plugin/`
- **Commands**: Run commands from or targeting `mkdocs-live-wysiwyg-plugin/` (e.g. `cd mkdocs-live-wysiwyg-plugin && ...`)

If a task requires changes outside this directory, ask the user for explicit permission first.
